OL,3,CMan, 50, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after woman found dead in Devon
OL,6,FA 50-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after a woman was
OL,8,Ffound dead at a property in Devon.
OL,10,FPolice and paramedics responded to a
OL,11,Freport of concern for the welfare of a
OL,12,Fwoman at an address in Hollam Way just
OL,13,Fbefore 10am on Saturday, 27 June.
OL,15,FA woman in her 30s was pronounced dead
OL,16,Fat the scene. Her next of kin are
OL,17,Fbeing supported by Devon and Cornwall
OL,18,FPolice.
