OL,3,CMan, 50, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after woman found dead in Devon
OL,6,FThe man arrested remains in custody.
OL,7,FEnquiries are ongoing, and officers
OL,8,Fremain at the scene.
OL,10,FWitnesses, or anyone with information
OL,11,For dashcam footage is asked to contact
OL,12,Fpolice on 101 quoting the reference
OL,13,Fnumber 50260165831.
